summary: This is a set of Dwemer metal textures that need to be finished. Silver with a bronze look with the right cube map. I'm color blind and can't finish the set. Help needed...
descriptionHtml: This is just a modders resource at the moment. Providing a new set of dwemer metal color to the game. For now it only contains the Dwemer metal sheet and Dwemer metal bars textures. No normal map provided. you can use any dwemer metal normal map with these and they still look right...
